@startuml
title Viaverse Chat / Messaging — Use Case Diagram
left to right direction

actor Requester
actor "Worker / Business" as Worker
actor "media-service" as Media
actor "Safety / Moderation" as Safety
actor "Support Admin" as Support

rectangle "Job / Quote Linked Messaging Boundary" {
  usecase "Create conversation\nfrom quote/job context" as Create
  usecase "Open conversation" as Open
  usecase "View context card\nrequest / quote / job" as Context
  usecase "Send message" as Send
  usecase "Detect contact/payment\nbypass attempt" as Detect
  usecase "Show safety warning\nor block" as Warn
  usecase "Attach media" as Attach
  usecase "Read messages" as Read
  usecase "Mark as read" as Mark
  usecase "Report message" as Report
  usecase "Block participant" as Block
  usecase "Escalate to support" as Escalate
  usecase "Audited support review" as AdminReview
}

Requester --> Open
Worker --> Open
Create --> Open
Open --> Context
Requester --> Send
Worker --> Send
Send ..> Detect : <<include>>
Detect --> Warn : if unsafe
Send ..> Attach : optional
Requester --> Read
Worker --> Read
Read --> Mark
Read --> Report
Report --> Block : optional
Report --> Escalate : if serious
Escalate --> AdminReview
Media --> Attach
Safety --> Detect
Support --> AdminReview

note bottom
Messaging is quote/job-linked, not generic social DM.
Contact sharing before allowed state is detected.
Support/admin review is scoped and audited.
end note
@enduml
